<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>V-GUARD AI Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0a192f; color: #ccd6f6; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        .hero-section { padding: 60px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #233554; text-align: center; }
        .profile-img { 
            width: 180px; height: 180px; border-radius: 50%; 
            border: 4px solid #64ffda; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1, h2, h3 { color: #64ffda; }
        .feature-card { 
            background: #112240; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; height: 100%; 
            border: 1px solid transparent; transition: 0.3s; 
        }
        .feature-card:hover { border-color: #64ffda; transform: translateY(-10px); }
        .feature-card i { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #64ffda; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .btn-cyber { 
            border: 1px solid #64ffda; color: #64ffda; padding: 10px 25px; 
            text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
        <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='erwin.jpg') }}" alt="Founder V-GUARD" class="profile-img">
        
        <h1>V-GUARD AI</h1>
        <div class="mt-4" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <h3>Visi & Misi</h3>
            <p><strong>Visi:</strong> Menjadi pionir keamanan digital berbasis AI yang adaptif untuk menjamin kedaulatan data bisnis global.</p>
            <p><strong>Misi:</strong> Memberikan proteksi siber proaktif dan manajemen keamanan cerdas bagi SME melalui dashboard terintegrasi.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="py-5 container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Fitur Layanan Produk</h2>
    <div class="row g-4 text-center">
        <div class="col-md-3"><div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-shield-virus"></i><h4>AI Threat Detection</h4><p class="small">Deteksi otomatis 24/7.</p></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-3"><div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-user-robot"></i><h4>Automatic Response</h4><p class="small">Mitigasi instan serangan.</p></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-3"><div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i><h4>Predictive Analysis</h4><p class="small">Analisis celah keamanan.</p></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-3"><div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-microchip"></i><h4>Endpoint Protection</h4><p class="small">Proteksi seluruh perangkat.</p></div></div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="container text-center py-5">
    <a href="/portal-klien" class="btn-cyber">Portal Klien</a>
    <a href="/admin-dashboard" class="btn-cyber">Admin Dashboard</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
